# Assets folder for InteliMaris website

Place images, icons, and other static assets here.

## Recommended Assets

### Icons
- Sensor type icons (water, fire, temperature, battery, GPS)
- Platform capability icons
- Navigation icons

### Illustrations
- Hero visual (marina with vessels and sensor network)
- Architecture diagram
- Dashboard mockup screenshots
- Sensor deployment flow

### Photography
- Vessel photos
- Marina facilities
- Sensor hardware
- Team photos (optional)

### Logos
- Primary logo (light/dark variants)
- Icon-only mark
- Horizontal lockup
- Vertical lockup

## File Naming Convention

- Use kebab-case: `sensor-water-icon.svg`
- Include size suffix for raster images: `hero-marina-2x.png`
- Use descriptive names: `screenshot-dashboard-fleet.png`
